ITEM NO.802               COURT NO.13               SECTION II
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition(s) for Special Leave to Appeal (Crl.)  No(s).  9484/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated  16-05-2025
in A528BNSS No. 15240/2025 passed by the High Court of Judicature 
at Allahabad]
PRANSHU & ORS.                                     Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
STATE OF U.P. & ANR.                               Respondent(s)
(FOR ADMISSION and I.R. )
 
Date : 07-07-2025 This petition was mentioned today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE RAJESH BINDAL
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE R. MAHADEVAN
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s) : 
Ms. Pallavi Pratap, AOR (Mentioned by)
                   
For Respondent(s) : 
Mr. Vishal Arun Mishra, AOR
                   
      UPON being mentioned the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
Learned  counsel  appearing  for  the  petitioners
mentioned the matter for correction of the typographical
error in the order dated 4th July, 2025 with regard to the
mentioning of the details of criminal case.
The correct number is as under:
‘Complaint  Case  No.12125  of  2024  registered  at
Police  Station  Kotwali  City,  District  Bijnor,  Uttar
Pradesh’.
1The same may be read in the order passed on 4 th
July, 2025 instead of FIR No.1293/2023 dated 29.12.2023.
(ANITA MALHOTRA)                           (SAPNA BANSAL)
     AR-CUM-PS                               COURT MASTER
